Total Recalls Most of Its Libya Workers Amid Safety Concerns

-- B y   M a r t h e   F o u r c a d e
-- 
2011-02-21T18:08:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/total-recalls-most-of-its-libya-workers-amid-safety-concerns.html
  Total SA ,  France ’s biggest explorer,
is asking most of its employees in  Libya  and their families to
leave the country amid safety concerns, a spokesman said.  The Paris-based company won’t say how many workers it has
in Libya and how many of those would leave, the spokesman,
Florent Segura, said by telephone today. Total is “monitoring
the situation closely,” he said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Marthe Fourcade at 
